metric.description: Current CPU utilization represented as a percentage of the reserved CPU that is currently in use. Values are typically numbers between 0.0 and 1.0 but might exceed 1.0. Charts display the values as a percentage between 0% and 100% or more. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_cpu_utilization

metric.description: Data utilization in bytes. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_disk_bytes_used

metric.description: Delta count of data disk read IO operations. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_disk_read_ops_count

layout.label: Network Connections - NEED TO INCLUDE POSTGRES

metric.description: Number of connections to databases on the Cloud SQL instance. Only applicable to MySQL and SQL Server. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_network_connections

metric.description: Delta count of data disk write IO operations. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_disk_write_ops_count

metric.description: Delta count of bytes received through the network. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_network_received_bytes_count

metric.description: Delta count of bytes sent through the network. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_network_sent_bytes_count

metric.description: Maximum data disk size in bytes. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_disk_quota

metric.description: Delta count of InnoDB pages written. Sampled every 60s and may take up to 210s to display.
metric.name: database_mysql_innodb_pages_written
